Title: Food or Floof
Description:
Look at this juicy and delectable herbed turtle meat! I speak objectively, of course. I'm a vegetarian.

Go on! He probably hasn't had a meal all day.
ObjectivesText: Bring the Herbed Turtle Meat and Glade Hoppers to Theramus.
RewardText: Oh dear. We heard his outburst. Are you okay?
